## noop variable

No-op / pass-through transducer, essentially the same as: `map(identity)`<!-- -->, but faster. Useful for testing and / or to keep existing values in a `multiplex()` tuple lane.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
noop: <T>() => Transducer<T, T>
```
